display_long_description:
Cactus Canyon Mini Golf 🌵⛳
Grab your putter and journey into the wild west of mini golf! Cactus Canyon brings players together in a fun, fast-paced multiplayer experience set across a dusty canyon and desert oasis.

Challenge your friends or team up in online multiplayer as you sink trick shots. Each hole is packed with surprises and wild west charm, making every round a new adventure.

Whether you’re lining up a perfect putt solo or laughing with friends across the course, Cactus Canyon Mini Golf is easy to pick up, tough to master, and always a blast.

Features:
	•	🎯 Themed holes inspired by the Wild West
	•	🌍 Online multiplayer with friends or players worldwide
	•	🤠 Interactive obstacles and trick shot challenges
	•	🕶️ Designed for an immersive VR mini golf experience

Dust off your boots, grab your putter, and see if you’ve got what it takes to conquer the canyon!
